KeysToEntries.1_9_1-01:
Sorry about this‥ dragging you
into a battle of amateurs like us‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-04:
Oh, by the way, Takumi's dad,
is he getting a new car？
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-05:
It looks like it. Takumi
said he'll buy a van or wagon
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-06:
Will that old man-like car be
something he'll drive, I wonder‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-07:
It's hard to imagine‥ Even though
he's called a legendary driver‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-08:
Well‥ maybe he can't
beat age after all‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-10:
What the heck‥ It's no
wonder he passed us so easily‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-11:
No way‼ Something fast
is coming from behind‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-12: No‥ no‥ way‥‼ This guy is‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-14: Why is there an Impreza here‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-15:
Damn‥ maybe we just can't
keep up after all‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_1-16:
It feels like we've had
a similar situation before‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-01:
Wataru‥ I know you understand,
but please don't get in the way
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-02: Don't give me that look‥ I know‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-03: I'll save the fun for later‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-05: You can tell just by a short run‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-07:
It flows so smoothly‥ I feel
like I'm being pulled in‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-08:
It's a miracle that
I'm barely keeping up‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-09: But‥ it shouldn't be like this‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-10:
Now show me‼ The true skill that
Ryosuke Takahashi saw potential in‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-12: All right‥ let's pass the baton‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-14: Heh‥ as expected‥ it turned out like this‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-15:
I'll show you the
power of the new engine‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-16:
Tch‥ still pulling off
flawless driving as always‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_2-17: I guess I was too late to start‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-01: Focus‥ I'll just run my own race‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-02:
Tch‼ This person‥
is quite skilled‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-03:
I can feel that he is
different from other street racers‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-04:
But, what I'm chasing
is not your back‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-07:
I've poured my entire life into
the pass, wanting to lead the group‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-08:
I absolutely don't want to lose‥
except to my Darling‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-10:
If I can keep going like this,
I can win‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-11:
It's incredible‥ What's
happening to me, I wonder‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-12:
Such a fulfilling feeling‥
it's been a while‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_3-13:
Oh no‥
I may have gone a bit too far‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-01:
Coming at me aggressively from
the beginning‥ a fierce one‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-03:
I hope that dangerous tightrope
act continues until the end‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-06:
Wataru and Takumi Fujiwara‥ they
didn't close in this fast before‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-07:
I can't go any further‥
it's too much
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-08: It's not logic‥ This is instinct‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-09: There are too many red lights‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-10:
Damn‥‼
What the hell are you doing‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-11: I'm told you‥ don't mess around‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-14:
This method is not what I want‥
but I won't give you a chance‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-15: I won't let you pass me‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_4-16:
We also have our
pride among comrades‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-03:
Tch‥ trying to pressure me‥
but I'm not going to fall for it‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-04:
Once we enter the slow
and medium speed section‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-05:
The difference in horsepower
is meaningless‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-07:
In street fights, the one
with the stronger heart wins‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-09:
But‥ if you lose your concentration,
you will make mistakes‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-10:
This is the crucial moment!!
Come on, Hachi-Roku Compressor‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-13:
I won't lose‼ In this situation,
it's a battle of motivation‥‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-14:
Isn't it in dramas that the
poor, hardworking one wins
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-15:
If I lose, there won't
be any excitement‼
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-16:
Damn‥ it feels like
I'm being provoked a lot‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-17: This is bad‥ I need to go all in‥
KeysToEntries.1_9_5-19:
Stopped just short
of the concrete wall‥
